section_title: Methodology for collection of International Transaction Log (ITL) fees
sentences: This issue (FCCC/TP/2010/1 and FCCC/SBI/2010/MISC.4) was first addressed by the SBI plenary on 31 May, and then considered in a contact group chaired by Toshiaki Nagata (Japan).
On 9 June, the SBI adopted conclusions and a draft COP/MOP decision.
